data.title: Gauri Pradhan Tejwani Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Gauri Pradhan Tejwani with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Participated in the 1998 Miss India competition, which launched her modelling career

Met her future husband Hiten Tejwani whilst shooting for a commercial

They later were cast opposite eachother in the TV series Kutumb

At the 2005 Indian Telly Awards she won the Best Supporting Actress award for her role in Kyuni Saas Bhi Kabhi Bahu Thi

Three-time winner of the STAR Parivaar Favourite Bahu Award, in 2006, 2007 and 2008

Has appeared in several reality TV shows along with her husband, including twice on dance show Nach Bailye, in 2006 and 2008
